title: Audio Adrenaline Discography 1993-2013 (19 Releases)

 * 1999 - Underdog
 * 2001 - Hit Parade
 * 2001 - Lift
 * 2003 - Worldwide
 * 2005 - Until My Heart Caves In
 * 2006 - Adios
 * 2007 - Farewell Concert - Live
 * 2008 - Greatest Hits
 * 2009 - The Ultimate Collection
 * 2012 - Kings And Queens - Single
 * 2013 - Big House To Ocean Floor
 * 2013 - King And Queens

Audio Adrenaline is a Christian rock band that formed in the mid 1980s.

Be Blessed,
